"font-family:宋体;\">北京时间</span><span> 17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：</span><span>30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">），涨幅</span><span>-0.31%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">今日伦敦金开盘</span><span> 1399.00 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">盎司，盘中最高到</span><span> 1408.35 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">盎司，最低到</span><span> 1396.50 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">盎司，截止现</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在</span><span> 1396.2560 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">盎司（北京时间</span><span> 17:30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">），涨幅</span><span>-0. 18% </span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【消息面】</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日本首相安倍晋三</span><span>(Shinzo\nAbe)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将于周三</span><span>(6 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span> <span>5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日</span><span>)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">稍晚发布新的经济改革方案，其中包括提高</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公共退休基金的股票持仓量目标。据参与制定改革计划的日本官员透露，政府将建议规模约</span> <span>112 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万亿</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span>(<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">约</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">合</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span>1.12<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亿</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span>)<span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">金</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">积</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">金</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">管</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">理</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">运</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">用</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">独</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">立</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">行</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">政</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">法</span><span><span>&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人</span> <span>(Government\nPension Investment Fund)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将更多资金配置到股票中，减少对国内债券的严重依赖。该</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">基金规模位居全球之首，目前资产组合中的债券和股票比重分别为</span> <span>67%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和</span> <span>11%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本日早间，美联储理事费舍尔在讲话中声称，美国目前不确定的财政政策会拖累美联储货币政策</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的实际效果，美国经济复苏改善效果良好，长期内的就业增长也备受期望。他表示美联储会对策略效</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">果进行评估，而后其货币政策可能会出现微幅调整。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美联储主席伯南克曾经表示，对于他们是否会在未来几次会议上开始削减刺激政策，主要决定于</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美国经济的复苏形势特别是就业数据能否切实好转，市场目前对美国经济数据的兴趣要远高于美联储</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">官员的讲话。本周内美国方面将出炉非农就业数据，显然更受市场关注，其结果会对美元情势产生较</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">大影响。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">晚间需要关注的数据有：</span><span>ADP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">就业人数、美国</span> <span>5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span> <span>ISM </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">非制造业指数</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【晚间操作建议】</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日内，白银市场高位回落，目前下探至</span> <span>4460 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">位置。该位置是强弱分界线，价格站稳该位置下方</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">则白银呈现弱势。晚间后市面临诸多消息公布，顺势交易即可。</span> <span>1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">多单：</span><span>4400-4420 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">反抽可进多，看向</span><span> 4460</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><span>4500.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">止损</span><span> 40 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点</span> <span>2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">空单：反弹不上破</span><span> 4500 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">可做空，看向</span><span> 4440</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">、</span><span>4380 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">附近。止损</span><span> 50 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点</span> <span>3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以防突发行情，实时操作请关注民泰实时解盘。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>&nbsp;</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span><br />\n</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><strong>免责声明：</strong></span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">民泰（天津）贵金属经营有限公司具有天津贵金属交易所综合会员资格，为该交易所第</span><span> 166 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">号会员单位。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本报告的作者是基于独立、客观、公正和审慎的原则制作本研究报告。本报告的信息均来源于公开资料