pan><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span>/ </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">千克，较前日涨幅为</span><span>-0.02%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【基本面】</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>1 <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">周四</span><span>(6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日</span><span>)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将迎来英央行、欧洲央行利率决议</span><span>.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目前市场普遍预计两央行均按兵不动。英国</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">央行此次决议，是金恩担任其行长的</span><span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">大结局</span><span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">之戏。市场预计在新行长卡尼即将上任之际，英国央</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">行将继续维持</span><span> QE </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">规模及利率不变。若决议符合市场预期，则英镑料将继续反弹走高；若意外扩大宽</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">松，料将令英镑大幅承压。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>2 <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">市场预期欧洲央行维持基准利率不变，重点关注随后的德拉基行长新闻发布会，若其措辞偏</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">向宽松，料将限制限制欧元短期上行空间。周四</span><span>(6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日</span><span>)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">利率决议上，德拉基是否会暗示类似的信息</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将受到密切关注。虽然欧洲央行会对再次降息措施慎之又慎，但相比于英国央行，欧洲央行存在更大</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">变数。</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>3 <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美国</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span> ADP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">就业人数增加</span><span>13.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万，高于前值</span><span>11.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万，但不及市场预期的</span><span>17.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万；美国</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-fa