=\"font-family:宋体;\">【基本面】</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>1<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">昨日英欧央行</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月利率决议均维持政策不变，与市场预期一致。德拉吉在随後的讲话中并没有做出进一步宽松的暗示，无形中为欧元提供支持</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>2<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">昨日公布的</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月份初请失业金人数平均值为</span><span>34.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万，高於</span><span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月均值</span><span>34.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万，初请失业金人数通常被视为就业市场的先导指标</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span>3 <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">目前市场焦点转向周五</span><span>(6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span>7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日</span><span>)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">美国非农数据，在美国一季度</span><span> GDP </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">下修且上周初请失业金人</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">数意外大涨后打压很快退出</span><span> QE </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的预期后，非农可能成为促使美联储减少购债的关键数据。目前市场</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">预期</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月非农人数增加</span><span>16.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万人，失业率料持稳</span><span>7.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，任何远离预期的数据结果都将令金融市场犹如</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">遭遇一场地震</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【今日操作建议】</span> \n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">白银盘整的整理区间</span><span>4380-4580</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">依然没有打破，接下来就看非农数据的结果来指引行情的方向</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">了，若非农数据大幅低于预期，对于白银会形成利好因素带动白银上涨，上方看的两个阻力位就在</span><span>4580 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">和</span><span>4650.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">若破位继续看涨</span><span>.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">反之白银则有望继续探底。短线做单