><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">千克，盘中上涨至 </span><span>4435 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">千克，最低至 </span><span>4299 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span>/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">千克，收盘于 </span><span>4374 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span>/ </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">千克，较前日涨幅为</span><span>+1.27%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【基本面】 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">1<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上周美国经济数据表现相对良好，且国际评级机构标普上调美国评级展望，但美元在 </span><span>FOMC </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">议<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">息会议前仍然承压，周线跌破</span><span>81.40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">关键支撑<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本周市场聚焦美联储</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月议息会议。</span><span>FOMC </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">将于北京时间本周四凌晨</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点发表政策声明，伯南克并将于</span><span>2:30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">召开新闻会。虽然享有“美联储传声筒”之称的华尔街记者表示美联储可能改变投资者的想法，但伯南克是否会带来意外之喜存在不确定性。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">英国央行本周也将公布会议纪要。鉴于现任行长金恩已期满，恰逢交接班之际，其他委员的<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">政策偏向可能对英镑近期产生直接指引<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【今日操作建议】 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">周一关注短期上方</span><span>4420</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">大阻力</span><span>4480</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的情况，而下方短线支撑在</span><span>4280-4300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这里，这一线也是上 周开盘后多次试探均为下破的地方。本周四美联储的利率决议将有望打破近一个月以来的区间震荡白 银会做一次方向的选择，日内操作上短线关注</span><span>4280-4420</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这个区间，高点做空在低点做多皆可。短线 做单注意风险严格带好止损操作。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天通银：</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span><span>1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">多单：在</span><span>4380-4400</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">附近做多，止损</span><span>4355</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，目标看</span><span>4400-4420 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">空单：在</span><span>4400-4420</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">附近做空，止损</span><span>4455</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，目标看</span><span>4420-4440</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以上建议为亚盘行情提供，亚盘建议多看少动，实时操作请关注民泰实时解盘。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">做单宜保护利润，严格止损。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">今日关注： <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">欧元区<span><span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月季调后贸易帐 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">欧元区<sp