明还是伯南克讲 话，都一改以往模凌两可的风格，基调变得极为清晰，即只要经济条件满足美联储制定的目标，最早\n在今年就有可能推出 </span><span>QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，看来美联储已经意识到了此前由于退出政策的模糊不清造成了金融市场的\n动荡最终会对美国经济的复苏进程产生影响，因此在市场的“逼宫行动”之下，美联储此次迫不得已 一改往日的风格，明确给出了未来可能的退出时间 <br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2<span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> 隔夜美国公布一连串经济数据。美国</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月谘商会领先指标月率上升</span><span>0.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，低於经济学家预期0.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，并低於前值</span><span>0.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，该指标通常用於衡量未来</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个月美国经济的表现，</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月制造业 </span><span>PMI </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">初值为</span><span>52.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">， 不及预期</span><span>52.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，均显示美国经济需要更多时间才能实现强劲增长。上周初请失业金人数意外上升</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万 至</span><span>35.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万，房产数据则继续向好，</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月成屋销售增长</span><span>4.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">至</span><span>518</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万 。<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3<span> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">周五（</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月</span><span>21</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">日）对于消息面而言，稍显清淡，日内仅有</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个加拿大数据有待公布，对贵金属市场影响也较为有限<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">【今日操作建议】 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">趋势是空头趋势到现在也没有改变，隔夜黄金下跌中继大三角形大幅破位，长中短期均线均呈\n现空头排列，非常明显的空头行情，千万不要盲目逆势做单非常危险，昨日盘面来看进场做多资金全 线被套<span><span>&nbsp; </span></span>。早盘注意</span><span>3930-50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的压力，下方看不到明显的支撑力度，盘口依然是逢高做空。短线做单注 意风险严格带好止损操作。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天通银：<span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span>1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">多单：以观望为主 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">空单：在</span><span>3930-3950</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">附近做空，止损</span><span>3980</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，目标看</span><span>3710-3730</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">以上建议为亚盘行情提供，亚盘建议多看少动，实时操作请关注民泰实时解盘。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">做单宜保护利润，严格止损。 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">今日关注： <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">08:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">欧元区欧盟财长会议 <span></span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">15:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">法国</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月份制造业采购经理人指数前值</span><span>46.4 </span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">15:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">法国</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">月份服务业采购经理人指数前值</span><span>44.3 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"p0\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=