管是指按照相关规定，由商业银行作为独立第三方，为交易客户建立客户交易结算资金明细账，通过银证转账实现客户交易结算资金的定向划转，对客户交易结算资金进行监管并对客户交易结算资金总额与明细账进行账务核对，以监控客户交易结算资金安全。</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">二、银行三方存管的特点：</span><span></span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">三方存管，资金安全</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">多渠道全网点服务，方便快捷</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">自由操作，可控性强</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">服务周到，便于监控</span><span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">三、银行三方存管开通流程：</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">银行三方存管开通流程如下：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">）工商银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a href=\"http://166jin.com/news/xyshow/343\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;</a></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><a href=\"http://166jin.com/news/xyshow/343\" target=\"_blank\">http://166jin.com/news/xyshow/343</a></span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">）光大银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><a href=\"http://166jin.com/news/xyshow/344\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;http://166jin.com/news/xyshow/344</a></span></span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;fon