span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司（北京时间</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">），较开盘微涨</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.66%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">今日伦敦银开盘</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">19.60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司，盘中最高到</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">19.83</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司，最低到</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">19.55</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司，截止现在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">19.66</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司（北京时间</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">17</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">45</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">），较开盘微涨</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.35%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">【消息面】</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、欧盟统计局</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Eurostat)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">公布的数据显示，欧元区</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月工业品出厂价格月率降幅大于预期。数据显示，欧元区</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月生产者物价指数</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(PPI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年率下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，预期为持平；月率下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，预期下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。按月比较，能源价格下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，半成品下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，耐用消费品和资本产品价格持平，非耐用消费品价格增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。除去能源价格分项后，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PPI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月率下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。而按年比较，能源价格下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，半成品下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，资本产品价格增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.6%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，耐用消费品价格增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，非耐用消费品价格增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。除去能源产品后，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PPI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年率增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、数据编撰机构</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Markit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">公布的数据显示，英国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月建筑业活动连续第二个出现增长，住房、商业地产和土木工程均有相对强势表现。数据显示，英国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Markit/CIPS</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">建筑业采购经理人指数</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(PMI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">录得</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">51.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，为连续第二个月处于荣枯分界线</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">上方，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">50.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Markit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">指出，总体建筑业产出受到了居住用房建筑活动的提振。同时，新订单增速创下了</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个月之最，预示未来建筑业有望享受更为快速的发展。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、周二</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亚太市场，澳洲联储</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(ReserveBankofAustralia)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">红布了最新一届货币政策例会，该行再次决定维持指标利率在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.75%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">的水平不变。澳洲联储同时表示，澳元汇率仍较高，可能有进一步放宽政策的空间，澳元可能会进一步走低。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、日本厚生劳动省周二</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">公布的数据显示，日本</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月劳动现金收入年率连续第二个月持平，表明首相安倍晋三</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(ShinzoAbe)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">刺激经济的举措尚未产生持续推动薪资增长的效果。数据表明，日本</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月加班工资年率下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，这暗示企业活动不太景气，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月为增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。此外，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月经常帐薪资年率下滑</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，降幅与上月相同；</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月特别加给年率增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4.5%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，上月为增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">【晚间操作建议】</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亚欧交易时段，现货白银呈现收敛的整理走势，但超短线价格走势极其偏弱，截至目前超短线都未能打开波动空间。当前来看，现货白银仍然延续上周五的反弹走势没有改变，整体银价的反弹走势保持的还较为完整，上方短线关键阻力位于</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">水平、下方短线的低点支撑位于</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3880</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">一线，综合日内的走势及基本面的信息来看，预计晚上北美时段银价探底回升的可能性较大。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天通银：</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">空单：银价反弹到</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4020</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">阻力受阻时空单进场，止损设在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4070</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">水平，目标看向</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3960</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">附近。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">多单：银价回落到</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3880</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">支撑企稳时多单进场，止损设在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3830</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">水平，目标看向</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3930</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">水平。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">【今日关注】</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">19</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">45</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美国上周</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">ICSC-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">高盛连锁店销售</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">55</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美国上周红皮书商业零售销售</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">22</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">00</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月工厂订单月率</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IBD</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">消费者信心指数</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">免责声明：</span><span></span></b> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">民泰（天津）贵金属经营有限公司具有天津贵金属交易所综合会员资格，为该交易所第</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">166</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">号会员单位。本报告的作者是基于独立、客观、公正和审慎的原则制作本研究报告。本报告的信息均来源于公开资料，作者对这些信息的准确性和完整性不作任何保证，也不保证所包含信息和建议不发生任何变更。作者已力求报告内容的客观、公正，但文中的观点、结论和建议仅供参考，不包含作者对贵金属价格涨跌或市场走势的确定性判断。报告中的信息或意见并不构成所述交易标的的买卖出价或征价，投资者据此做出的任何投资决策与我司无关。本报告版权为民泰（天津）贵金属共有，未经书面许可，任何机构和个人不得以任何形式翻版、复制和发布。如引用须注明出处为民泰贵金属，且不得对本报告进行有悖原意的引用、删节和修改。刊载或者转发本研究报告或其内容摘要的，应当注明本报告的发布人和发布日期，并提示使用本研究报告的风险。未经授权刊载或者转发本报告的，我司将保留向其追究法律责任的权利。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','2013-07-03 08:07:48','本站原创',NULL,1,'2013-7-2 17:48:15 ',1,'当前来看，现货白银仍然延续上周五的反弹走势没有改变，整体银价的反弹走势保持的还较为完整，上方短线关键阻力位于4020水平、下方短线的低点支撑位于3880一线，综合日内的走势及基本面的信息来看，预计晚上北美时段银价探底回升的可能性较大。','07/02','原创研究'),(297,'Comex期金周二小幅下滑，因美元表现强势','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">因今日公布的美国经济数据总体向好，提振美元，同时也暗示美联储可能提早退出</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，金价承压下行。分析人士指出之前的上涨源于季前的空头回补，未来金价的上扬依然要仰仗投资者的买兴。如果金价能在未来限制跌幅，则能吸引更多投资者回归金市。然而当前市场关注的重点还是在欧洲货币政策决议以及美国非农就业数据的公布，料能为金价未来的走势给予指引。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Comex</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">期金周二下跌</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">12.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元，报</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1243.40</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　美国商务部</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(DOC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二发布报告称，美国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月工厂订单月率为增加</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.1%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，前值为增</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，预估值增加</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.0%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，略高于预期，显示美国经济动能向好。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　美国经济研究机构</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Johnson Redbook</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二公布的数据显示，美国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日当周红皮书连锁店销售年率增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，上周为增长</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.8%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　道明证券</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(TD Securities)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周一</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">宣布下调</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年和</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年黄金价格预期，原因是美联储</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(FED)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">即将撤走支撑金价的量化宽松</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(QE)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">措施。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　美银美林</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Bank of American Merrill Lynch)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">分析师周二表示，排除之前作出金价将在未来跌至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司的可能性，因目前金价逐渐开始企稳。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　该行还称，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">尽管我们不认为未来会有更多投资者入驻黄金市场，但近期金价的表现暗示未来短期的下行风险已经开始受到抑制。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　花旗集团</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Citi)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">期货分析师</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Sterling Smith</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二表示，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">今日公布的美国经济数据可能令黄金稍稍承压，同时也暗示美国经济改善良好，刺激美联储提前退出</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　法国兴业银行</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Societe Generale)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">的金属分析师</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Robin Bhar</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">表示，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">目前金价的反弹纯粹是由空头回补引发。投资者们将转而关注，后续的经济数据，以及数据会如何影响</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">FOMC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">的政策决定。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Bhar</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">警告称，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">金价的反弹不可能持续很久，几个最终还会跌向</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1000</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">他补充道，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">只要经济复苏，美元预计将会在下半年继续走强。黄金跌势的大潮可能会减弱，但至少短期内不会。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　一位香港交易员在接受采访时表示，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">黄金要想重获投资者信任，至少需要在目前水平企稳几个交易日。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　花旗集团</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Citi)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">期货分析师</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">Sterling Smith</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二表示，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">今日公布的美国经济数据可能令黄金稍稍承压，同时也暗示美国经济改善良好，刺激美联储提前退出</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　瑞银集团</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(UBS)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">周二在新加坡为一些需求财富管理的客户开设了黄金金库服务，引起了当地投资者广泛的兴趣，尽管目前黄金已跌入熊市。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　加拿大丰业银行</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Scotia)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">表示，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">预计未来金价将出现上涨。目前主要支撑位置在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元，该位置是上周五</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">所触及的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月低点，因季末市场出现大量的清算行为。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　投资大亨罗杰斯</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(Jim Rogers)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">则认为，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">上周五金价大跌是因为投资者被迫平仓。有大量高杠杆炒家现在正被迫出售他们的黄金持仓。一般情况下，当出现这种被迫平仓情况的时候，市场就已经接近价格底部了。这可能不是最终的底部，但明显是接近底部了。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　全球最大的黄金</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">ETF--SPDR Gold Trust</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">截至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日的黄金持仓量减少</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">吨，至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">968.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">吨。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　全球最大的白银</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">ETF--iShares Silver Trust</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">截至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日的白银持仓量维持在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9,905.88</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">吨不变</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','2013-07-03 10:07:57','本站原创',NULL,3,'2013-7-3 9:13:31',1,'如果金价能在未来限制跌幅，则能吸引更多投资者回归金市。然而当前市场关注的重点还是在欧洲货币政策决议以及美国非农就业数据的公布，料能为金价未来的走势给予指引。','07/03','分析评论'),(298,'希腊坏了“一锅粥”，美元依旧强势','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">【基本面】</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　欧洲</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　欧盟统计局在一份声明中称，计算出现错误是因为法国数据有误，导致法国失业率被低估0.5个百分点，欧元区整体失业率则低估了0.1个百分点，欧元区5月失业率为12.2%，而不是周一(7月1日)公布的12.1%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　数名欧元区官员周二表示，希腊还有三天时间，来向其债权人证明该国能够满足国际救助的附加条件，以便获得下一笔救助贷款。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　希腊政府与贷款机构周一就拨付81亿欧元救助贷款恢复谈判，此前谈判中断了两周，期间希腊政府差点倒台，因为关闭希腊国家广播电视公司(ERT)引发政府内部矛盾。一名参与谈判的欧元区高层官员表示，对于希腊改革公共部门的进展，例如税收或医保服务等等，债权人普遍感到不满。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　美国</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　周二数据显示，美国5月工厂订单月率上升2.1%，预期上升2.0%，前值修正为上升1.3%，初值上升1.0%。工厂订单的增加受到了对飞机需求上升的推动，但对于其他用品需求仅温和上升。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　纽约联储主席杜德利周二重申了他此前对美联储政策前景状况所表述的看法，表示尽管市场各界对美联储可能提前结束购债这一状况已有非常的担心，但实际上，美联储可能会在未来相当一段时间内都继续维持当前的宽松措施力度，来为经济复苏提供进一步的支持。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　美联储理事鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)周二表示，鉴于当前美国失业率仍然高企，且整体通胀率也已明显低于目标控制水平，美联储当前每月收购850亿美元债券的量化宽松措施(QE)或将继续维持相当一段时间。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　总结</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　欧元区失业率创1995年以来最高水平，加上希腊的不稳定因素令欧元承压下行，本应该提升黄金的避险魅力，但是由于美国5月工厂订单较4月增加，且增幅高于市场预期，显示出在萧条的冬季过后，企业正逐渐加大开支，使美元得到提振；尽管盘中美联储杜德利、鲍威尔均表示当前QE力度或将延续相当一段时间，不过美元强势并未受到打压，使得金银承压下行。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　周三美国ADP就业报告亦值得投资者关注。经济学家预期6月ADP新增就业人数为16万，远高于前值13.5万，由于ADP和非农就业人数在长期中高度正相关，向好的结果将提升投资者对就业市场的乐观预期，或为美元提供上行动能。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　ETF持仓</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　黄金</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　白银</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　ETF上周黄金持仓量持续减少，白银持仓未有变化，可以看出目前机构对金银未来看空的想法较强，并未出现看多的情绪。</span>\n</p>\n<a href=\"http://i1.cnfolimg.com/money/66_1764666.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i1.cnfolimg.com/money/66_1764666.png\" style=\"border:medium none;\" align=\"middle\" border=\"0\" width=\"500\" /></a><a href=\"http://i0.cnfolimg.com/money/67_1764667.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i0.cnfolimg.com/money/67_1764667.png\" style=\"border:medium none;\" align=\"middle\" border=\"0\" width=\"500\" /></a>','2013-07-03 10:07:28','本站原创',NULL,3,'2013-07-03 10:07:28',1,'尽管盘中美联储杜德利、鲍威尔均表示当前QE力度或将延续相当一段时间，不过美元强势并未受到打压，使得金银承压下行。','07/03','分析评论'),(299,'非农前夕谨慎做空，白银反弹形态明显','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">一、基本面：</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　由欧盟委员会、欧洲央行和国际货币基金组织</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(IMF)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">所组成的三驾马车官员</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">日重返希腊，以便重新评估希腊的援助改革执行情况。如果评估结果正面，该国将会获得</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">81</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">亿欧元下一笔援助金。有消息称，斯托纳拉斯将在北京时间</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">22:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">同三驾马车的代表举行首次会谈。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　美国供应管理协会</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(ISM)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周一公布的数据显示，美国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ISM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">制造业活动指数上涨，从上个月意外萎缩中上扬，但是就业指数为接近</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年累最低值。数据显示，美国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ISM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">制造业采购经理人指数</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">50.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，预估</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">50.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，前值为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">49.0</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">。美国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ISM</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">就业指数</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">48.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，预估</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">50.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2009</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年来最低。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　汇丰银行</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(HSBC)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">和数据编撰机构</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Markit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周一联合公布的数据显示，中国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月制造业采购经理人指数</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(PMI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">终值降至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">48.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，创九个月最低水准，低于预览值</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">48.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">和</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月终值</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">49.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">。但是中国国家统计局和物流与采购联合会</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(CFLP)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周一联合公布的数据显示，中国宏观经济先行指标</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">--6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月官方制造业采购经理人指数</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(PMI)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">回落至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">50.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，上月官方