>)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">公布的数据显示，英国服务业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月成长速度为逾两年来最快，提振经济乐观看法，为英国央行</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(BOE)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">新任主席卡尼</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(MarkCarney)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">带来更多好消息。服务业新订单成长速度为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2007</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月以来最快，显示景气回暖情况或许能持续，另外，民间部门活动的整体数据亦显示，第二季经济成长稳健。继周一公布强劲的制造业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">之后，数据显示英国经济可能不再需要更多刺激就能达成新任央行主席卡尼所形容的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">逃逸速度</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、澳大利亚统计局周三</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">公布的数据显示，澳大利亚</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月经季调后商品</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">服务贸易帐盈余为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亿澳元，上月为盈余</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.71</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亿澳元。此前接受媒体调查的经济学家的预期中值显示，澳洲</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月经季调后商品</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">服务贸易帐料持平。澳大利亚</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月经季调后商品</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">服务出口月率上升</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，进口则上升</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。具体数据表明，澳大利亚</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月整体出口金额为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">264.44</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亿澳元，高于上月的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">255.30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亿澳元；</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月整体进口金额为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">257.74</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亿澳元，上月为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">253.60</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亿澳元。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">【晚间操作建议】</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">亚欧交易时段，现货白银继续维持高位弱势整理的走势，虽然盘中银价上冲下杀、短线多空争夺激烈，但超短线价格走势仍然迷惘、没有明确的方向，截至目前超短线都未能打开波动空间。当前来看，现货白银仍然延续上周五反弹之后的整理走势为主，整体银价的短线走势方向缺乏，上方短线关键阻力位于</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3940</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">水平、下方短线的低点支撑位于</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3820</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">一线，预计晚间银价继续保持在该区间内整理的可能性较大。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天通银：</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.</span><span style=\"font-family