an><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">300%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">多！亲身验证了贵金属投资的魅力！（点击可看大图）</span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/TAB1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/TAB1.jpg\" style=\"border:none;width:666px;height:260px;\" /></a>','2013-07-04 09:07:03','本站原创',NULL,2,'2013-7-3 16:52:31',1,'六月初入夏季，白银出现单边下跌行情，市场有波动就有获利机会！六月民泰涌现出一位神级客户，以小资金博取了大收益','07/03','盘面播报'),(305,'6月非制造业PMI 降至9个月新低','<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">在制造业活动面临萎缩的同时，非制造业活动也进一步降温。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月官方非制造业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">降至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">53.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，创</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个月来最低，汇丰服务业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">与上月基本持平，仍在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月创下的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个月低位附近徘徊，这表明经济下行压力有增无减。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　中国物流与采购联合会、国家统计局昨日公布数据显示，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月份中国非制造业商务活动指数</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">53.9%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，环比下降</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">0.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个百分点。尽管该指数仍处于荣枯分水岭上方，但今年以来该指数持续下滑。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　而同一天公布的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月汇丰服务业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">指数为</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">51.3%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">，几乎与</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">51.2%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">的数据持平。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">中国服务业的潜在增长动力仍然疲软，制造业也面临同样的情况。由于新订单的增长仍然低迷，就业的增长也承受巨大压力。而增值税改革尚需时间才能显现效果，因此在未来几个月中服务业活动有可能会进一步降温。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">汇丰大中华区首席经济学家屈宏斌说。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　稍早公布的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月官方制造业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">和汇丰制造业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">双双下滑，前者降至逼近荣枯线，而后者则连续两个月处在荣枯线下方，显示制造业活动疲软，经济下行压力加大。而此次非制造业活动也不尽乐观，可见经济下行压力有增无减。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　国家统计局将于</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日召开二季度经济运行情况新闻发布会，届时将公布二季度</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">GDP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">在内的一系列宏观经济数据。种种迹象显示，二季度经济增速或在一季度</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7.7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">的基础上继续放缓。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　不过，专家也指出，由于劳动力、环境、资源、能源等多种要素制约，我国经济转型已经迫在眉睫，国家将更强调经济增长质量，而调结构必然要遭受经济增速下滑的阵痛。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　中国物流与采购联合会副会长蔡进指出，二季度制造业</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">和非制造业的商务活动指数均保持在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">50%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">以上，反映出当前中国经济延续了平稳增长的基本特征。经济发展体现出稳增长和调结构的双重效果。</span> \n</p>','2013-07-04 09:07:16','本站原创',NULL,4,'2013-07-04 09:07:16',1,'　','07/04','市场要闻'),(306,'【热门议题】黄金投资：成本价≠止跌价','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">今年以来，不断下跌的金价已累计下挫近三成，继</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月中旬暴跌后，上半年最后一个交易日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">(6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">国际金价更是跌至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元／盎司成本价区间。金价再次走低，“挑”动国内部分“中国大妈”们再次出手抄底补仓。业内专家提醒投资者，“成本价”不一定是“止跌价”，“急刹车”后金价仍有下“砸”空间，投资风险大。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">金千二“成本价”甩卖</span></b></span><b><span><br />\n</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　今年</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月以来，黄金遭遇大规模抛售，金价一度创下</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年来最大跌幅，整个第二季度金价更是创下</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1920</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年以来的最差纪录。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">日，上半年最后一个交易日，伦敦现货黄金盘中报出</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1180</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元／盎司，失守</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">大关。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　“全球平均采金成本在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">950</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">盎司，国际金价正在不断接近黄金矿产开采的综合生产成本。”上海黄金交易所专家顾问李骏说，从美联储主席伯南克宣布今年提前放缓</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">QE3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">步伐，并计划在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年中期全面退出量化宽松政策的消息传出后，美元走强趋势明显，对金价形成更大的下行压力。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　随着金价的持续走低，包括高盛、德意志、汇丰、瑞银、摩根士丹利、法国兴业银行等多家国际金融机构相继下调金价预期。高盛更是将</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年黄金均价下调至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">年黄金均价下调至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1050</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　业内专家表示，虽然黄金价格是全球金融市场交易的结果，金矿并不具有定价权，但金价低于开采价格“甩卖”，将压榨黄金生产商利润，使其面临停产歇业风险，并由此导致生产商逐渐减产来应对日益增长的成本支出。</span><span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><strong>　“中国大妈”再出手</strong></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　金价不断下挫，让多数</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月底抢购黄金饰品的“中国大妈”被套牢。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月以来，“中国大妈”们一直“按兵不动”，但当国际金价</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月底跌至“成本价”后，各地的“中国大妈”们有些按捺不住。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　据综合媒体报道，黄金价格上周末再次大跌后，南京、广州、长沙等地金店内人气渐旺，虽然没有出现一些“豪单”“大单”，但出现了不少“阶梯式”购金的市民，虽然每次购金量不多，但购金频率较高，隔三差五地就会来买一些。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　“主要是希望趁跌补货，摊薄成本。”南京市民张女士说，“我在今年</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月份黄金暴跌时买了</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">克黄金，当时以为抄到底了，没想到现在金价更低了。如果今后金价再跌得厉害，我还会出手再买一点，以平衡成本。”</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　“现在金价已跌到</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元／盎司了，还能怎么跌下去？”在不少“中国大妈”们看来，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">美元／盎司附近的成本价就是金价“底线”，此时不买更待何时？</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　记者采访了解到，虽然黄金饰品消费者和实物金条投资者的抢购热情明显降温，但“中国大妈”们购买黄金的热情并没有降至冰点，其消费和投资理念与方式更趋向理性。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">金价有下“砸”空间</span></b><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　“成本价不是止跌价，也不是底线价。”李骏说，不要以为跌到了成本价就不会再往下跌，虽然在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月底暴跌后国际金价在本周一、二连续两个交易日收阳，给疲软不堪的金价带来曙光，但这波回调难改金价下跌大势。当前美国经济数据总体向好，美元走强，黄金价格未来必定承压下行。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　采访中，多数专家表示“坚决”看空，认为金价下行趋势不会因为短暂的反弹而发生改变。“当前市场关注的重点是欧洲货币政策决议以及美国非农就业数据的公布，这些消息的好坏将为下半年为现货金价走势给出指引。”</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　黄金虽然在消费市场有些许“失宠”，但不断走低的金价还是让不少投资者看到了投资机会，他们认为在全球货币滥发的大背景下，黄金仍不失为一种很好的抗通胀工具。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　今年以来，黄金作为对冲通货膨胀和货币贬值风险工具的吸引力逐渐减弱，未来中长期看，金价跌势难改。因此，投资者除了选择更加灵活的投资方式，也可尝试短期投资，即抓住每天价格的小波动做投资，而不是做长期买卖。</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','2013-07-04 09:07:58','本站原创',NULL,4,'2013-07-04 09:07:58',1,'　黄金虽然在消费市场有些许“失宠”，但不断走低的金价还是让不少投资者看到了投资机会，他们认为在全球货币滥发的大背景下，黄金仍不失为一种很好的抗通胀工具。','07/04','市场要闻'),(307,'国际金价涨近1% 投资者为周五非农数据做准备','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">纽约汇市周三(7月3日)，国际金价涨近1%，受葡萄牙和埃及政治危机影响，投资者起初纷纷买入黄金以求避险。此外一项衡量美国非制造业的关键数据意外下降也在早些时候提振黄金价格走高。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　葡萄牙外交部长Paulo Portas周二辞职，而财政部长加斯帕尔(Vito Gaspar)则于前一天辞职。Portas是葡萄牙人民党的领袖，该政党是葡萄牙联合政府的关键伙伴。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　葡萄牙的政治闹剧又一次提醒市场欧元区主权债务危机尚未解决。受相关担忧影响，葡萄牙股市与债市下跌，希腊、西班牙与意大利债市也走低。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　在投资者对经济或政治动荡感到担忧时，金价一般会出现上涨。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　</span><b>卖盘稳步抵消避险买盘</b><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　不过积极消息方面，6月份非制造业就业指数从5月份的50.1升至54.7；而6月份美国私营部门就业人数增加188,000人，增幅高于预期；上周首次申请失业救济人数也意外减少5,000人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　这些数据均显示出美国就业市场前景看转，令投资者对于美联储退出货币刺激政策时间的争论有所升温。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　由于上述数据显示出较为积极的前景，资金从黄金转移至股市，由此引发的卖盘稳步抵消了避险买盘。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　</span><b>非农先导</b><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　美国6月份私营部门就业数据好于预期，而劳工部公布的上周首次申请失业救济人数也有所下降。市场将这些数据视为周五非农就业数据的重要先导。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　在这些数据之后，关键的美国非农就业数据将于周五公布，该数据是影响美联储货币政策前景的关键因素之一。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　经济学家们目前预计，周五公布的6月份非农就业人数或增加160,000人，5月份为增加175,000人。失业率或从7.6%小幅降至7.5%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　美国市场今日于美东时间下午2点提前收盘，周四将因适逢独立日而休市，假日前投资者不愿大举建仓。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　</span><b>持仓变动</b><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-family:SimSun, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:24px;color:#333333;\">　　全球最大的黄金支持的上市交易基金SPDR Gold Trust 周二黄金持仓量减少0.37%，至964.69吨，此为2009年2月以来新低。</span> \n</p>','2013-07-04 09:07:09','本站原创',NULL,4,'2013-07-04 09:07:09',1,'数据显示出美国就业市场前景看转，令投资者对于美联储退出货币刺激政策时间的争论有所升温。  　　由于上述数据显示出较为积极的前景，资金从黄金转移至股市，由此引发的卖盘稳步抵消了避险买盘。','07/04','市场要闻'),(308,'Comex期金周三小幅上涨，因美元美股双双走跌','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">因今日公布的美国数据参差不齐，加之欧洲数据向好，美元及美股承压下跌。同时欧洲多国债务危机持续发酵，葡萄牙政治格局出现动荡，该国外长、财长相继辞职，国债收益率飙升逾</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">7%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，刺激市场避险情绪上升，金价获得买盘支撑震荡上扬。另外，埃及政治冲突也出现升级，将避险情绪进一步推高。目前市场正密切关注周五公布的美国非农数据，料将对金价的走势起到决定性作用。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Comex</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">期金周三上涨</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">8.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">美元，报</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">1251.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">盎司。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　美国劳工部</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(DOL)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周三公布的数据显示，美国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">29</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">日当周初请失业金人数为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">34.3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">万人，预期为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">34.5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">万。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　美国自动数据处理公司</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ADP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周三表示，美国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ADP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">私营部门就业为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">18.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">万人，预期为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">万人，超出预期。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　数据编撰机构</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Markit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周三公布的数据显示，欧元区</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Markit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">综合</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">PMI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">终值为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">48.7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，预估为</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">48.9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">，终值略微下修，不及预期，但仍然录得近</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">个月新高。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　葡萄牙当地媒体报道称，葡萄牙外长、该国联合政府的第二大党派领导人</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Paulo Portas</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">于周二</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">日</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">辞职。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Portas</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">是该国右翼人民党的领导人，并且他的辞职紧随财长加斯帕昨日的辞职之后。没有人民党的领导，现在的中右翼政府将会失去其在议会的占大多数议席的地位。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　葡萄牙</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年期公债收益率升至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2012</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月来最高，因该国政治紧张形势升级，促使投资者抛售风险较高且评级较低的债券。该国</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年期公债收益率日内上涨</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">110</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">个基点，报</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">7.62%</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Marex North America LLC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">经纪人</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Carlos Perez-Santalla</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周三表示，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">欧洲的债务危机再度显现，这刺激了人们的避险情绪。同时因埃及冲突升级，投资者也逐渐开始回归金市。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">VTB Capital</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">分析师</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Andrey Kryuchenkov</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">表示，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">今日金价上涨的主要动力来自于美元和美股的走低，这是由于欧元区数据良好，美国经济数据不够清晰以及对葡萄牙和希腊经济危机担忧所造成的。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Kryuchenkov</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">还称，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">目前交易量很低，所以我不认为交易商会在美国非农数据公布前轻易行动，毕竟这在本周数据里是重中之重，另外美国明年休假也是影响市场清淡的因素之一。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Macquarie Secutiries</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">分析师</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Matt Turner</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周三表示，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">由于近期金价出现转机，我们也稍微转变了看法。我们现在预计金价将在</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年年底上涨至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">1370</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">盎司。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Turner</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">指出，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">由于市场对美联储退出</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">的臆测过度，导致金价在之前严重受挫，但我们的经济学家认为美联储不会在</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年末或</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2015</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年前就退出</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">QE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">。目前市场似乎有些过于偏空，美国纽约商品交易所黄金期货的净多头头寸减少至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2002</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">年来最低水平。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　美银美林</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(Merrill Lynch)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">分析师</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">Michael Widmer</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">表示，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">如果周五公布的非农数据向好，美联储很可能会提前缩减购债，加之通胀压力并不是很大，对黄金而言是个巨大的利空消息。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　投资大鳄加特曼</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">(Dennis Gartman)</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">周三表示，</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">近期黄金遭到无情地抛售，但就本周金价的表现看，我认为金价未来可能上涨。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">加特曼曾在上周指出金价可能会跌向</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">900</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">美元</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">盎司。虽然现在我不认为金价会继续下跌，但世事难料，不过我觉得黄金最糟糕的日子确实已经过去了。</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">\"</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　全球最大的黄金</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ETF--SPDR Gold Trust</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">截至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">日的黄金持仓量减少</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">3.61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">吨，至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">964.69</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">吨。</span></span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:white;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　全球最大的白银</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">ETF--iShares Silver Trust</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">截至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">月</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">日的白银持仓量增加</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">55.54</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">吨，至</span><span style=\"background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">9,961.42</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;background:none repeat scroll 0% 0% white;font-size:16px;\">吨。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','2013-07-04 09:07:42','本站原创',NULL,3,'2013-07-04 09:07:42',1,'因今日公布的美国数据参差不齐，加之欧洲数据向好，美元及美股承压下跌。同时欧洲多国债务危机持续发酵，葡萄牙政治格局出现动荡，该国外长、财长相继辞职，国债收益率飙升逾7%，刺激市场避险情绪上升，金价获得买盘支撑震荡上扬。','07/04','分析评论'),(309,'避险情绪升温 金价跌势放缓','<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">葡萄牙先后有内阁包括财长因财政紧缩问题请辞，希腊仍未就包括公共部门改革之外的议题在周一欧元集团会议之前与国际救助方达成协议，市场忧虑欧债危机重燃，葡萄牙等欧猪国债收益率显著上扬。同时埃及政局以至中国经济放缓亦造成市场困扰。</span><span><br />\n<br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">　　美国</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">月私人市场就业职位增加</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">18.8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">万个，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5</span><