4px;font-weight:bold;\">\n				(点击图片，放大查看)\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:18px;color:blue;font-weight:bold;\">\n				六：最后银行转天津贵交所（入金），出现下面的界面后，填写阳光卡号，交易资金账户，转账金额和阳光卡的密码，点击确定。\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;\">\n				<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/gd/6.jpg\"><img alt=\"点击查看大图\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/gd/6.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a> \n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;\">\n				(点击图片，放大查看)\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>','2013-07-05 15:07:25','本站原创',NULL,12,'2013-07-05 15:07:25',1,'光大银行可以足不出户，完成天津贵金属交易所贵金属投资的网上签约。具体签约流程，如下图所示：','07/05','常见问题'),(346,'华夏银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程','<p align=\"center\">\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" height=\"500\" width=\"402\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">华夏银行的签约、解约、资金往来等业务办理时间：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9:30</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">—</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">20:00</span></b> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">客户获取天津贵金属交易所交易席位号</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">即会员将客户</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">位交易帐号，</span><span style=\"color:red;font-size:16px;\">在后台做过预签约</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">) </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">后，即可到华夏银行网点办理签约业务；</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户可以在同城任一网点办理签约；</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户只能在开户网点办理签约。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span></b> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">特别提示：天津贵金属交易所交易在华夏银行代码为：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\">600010</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span></span></b> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>使</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>用</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>手</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>册</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>查</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>看</strong></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>：</strong></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://166mintai.com/news/show/347\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">《华夏银行B2B大宗三方存管模式交易商使用手</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">册》</span></a> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>表格文档查看：</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">华夏银行申请表1</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/hx_1.jpg\"><img alt=\"华夏银行申请表1\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/hx_1.jpg\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">华夏银行申请表2</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/hx_2.jpg\"><img alt=\"华夏银行申请表2\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/hx_2.jpg\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">存管协议书</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<span id=\"__kindeditor_bookmark_start_10__\"></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<a href=\"http://www.91jin.com/UserFiles/hxcg.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/resources/editor/attached/image/20130705/20130705082758_83520.gif\" alt=\"\" /></a> \n</p>','2013-07-05 16:07:38','本站原创',NULL,12,'2013-07-05 16:07:38',1,'','07/05','常见问题'),(347,'华夏银行B2B大宗三方存管模式交易商使用手册','<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;color:#000000;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:2em;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">客户获取天津贵金属交易所交易席位号 (即会员将客户15位交易帐号，在后台做过预签约) 后，即可到华夏银行网点办理签约业务；个人客户可以在同城任一网点办理签约，企业客户只能在开户网点办理签约。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">特别提示：天津贵金属交易所交易在华夏银行代码为：600010。</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">一、柜台操作</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（一）签约、解约、变更</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1、要求客户提交以下资料：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（1）填写完整、经法人授权并盖章的《华夏银行、天津贵金属交易所有限公司、投资人交易资金三方存管协议》及《华夏银行电子商务交易客户申请表》；</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（2）客户为单位的，提供法人、经办人身份证原件和加盖公章的复印件；客户为个人的提供身份证原件及复印件。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">二、网银操作（只能进行</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">出入金及出入金查询</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">操作）</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（一）登陆网页：</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交易商把“华夏盾”插在电脑上，自动回显网页（如下），请选择“B2B网上支付”登陆地址：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx1.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx1.png\" style=\"border:none;\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交易商请选择“大宗三方存管模式”----证书版交易商登陆：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx2.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx2.png\" style=\"border:none;\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交易商请选择选择证书点击“确定”按钮，并在回显页面输入“华夏盾密码”：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx3.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx3.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;color:#000000;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">\n	<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx4.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx4.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交易商进入“大宗三方存管平台”，按要求填写登陆信息，进入交易界面：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx5.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx5.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（二）出入金操作</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1、入金</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">操作流程如下：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">点击入金菜单，系统将显示交易商绑定账户信息及余额，输入入金金额，点击“确定”：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx6.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx6.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">核对并确认入金信息，点击“确定”：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx7.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx7.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">选择证书进行签名：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx8.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx8.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">输入PIN码，点击“确定”：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx9.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx9.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">入金提交成功，等待复核（企业交易商可在办理签约时设置是否需要符合，个人交易商不需要复核）：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx10.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx10.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">另外一个操作员登录后首页会有“入金复核”提示，也可点击复核菜单，使用“入金复核”功能进行复核。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx11.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx11.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">点击“查看入金详细信息”：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx12.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx12.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">点击“同意”，提示选择证书进行签名：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx13.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx13.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">输入PIN码</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx14.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx14.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">入金复核通过，入金成功：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx15.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx15.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2、出金</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">出金申请操作流程如下：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">点击出金申请菜单，系统将显示账户余额、可出资金，以及绑定账户信息，输入出金金额：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx16.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx16.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">确认出金信息：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx17.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx17.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">证书签名：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx18.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx18.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">输入PIN码：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx18-5.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx18-5.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">出金提交成功，等待复核（企业交易商可在办理签约时设置是否需要复核，个人交易商不需要复核）：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx19.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx19.png\" style=\"border:none;\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">使用另外一个操作员登录并复核，交易市场审核通过后出金成功，大宗三方存管平台将自动发送出金申请成功短信给交易商指定的手机号码：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx21.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx21.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">复核 略</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">（三）出入金查询</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1、入金历史查询</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">入金历史查询用于查询指定时间范围内，交易商通过大宗三方存管平台进行入金的历史记录。操作流程如下：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">点击菜单栏的“查询”下的“入金历史查询”，选择时间范围和状态，点击“查询”，界面显示如下图：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx22.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx22.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">查询结果页面如下图所示：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx23.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx23.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2、出金历史查询</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">出金历史查询用于查询指定时间范围内，交易商通过大宗三方存管平台进行出金的历史记录。操作流程如下：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">点击菜单栏的“查询”下的“出金历史查询”，选择时间范围和状态，点击“查询”，界面显示如下图：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx24.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx24.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">查询结果页面如下图所示：</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx25.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/hx25.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','2013-07-05 16:07:47','本站原创',NULL,12,'2013-07-05 16:07:47',1,'客户获取天津贵金属交易所交易席位号 (即会员将客户15位交易帐号，在后台做过预签约) 后，即可到华夏银行网点办理签约业务；个人客户可以在同城任一网点办理签约，企业客户只能在开户网点办理签约。','07/05','常见问题'),(348,'中信银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程','<div align=\"center\">\n	<p>\n		<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" height=\"400\" width=\"442\" />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p align=\"left\">\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天津贵金属交易所在中信银行系统的市场代码为：</span><b><span style=\"color:red;font-size:16px;\">10090000</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">中信银行签约业务受理的时间为：</span><span></span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">08:35</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">17:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">■个人客户签约流程</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">．个人客户签约</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程：</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户本人持有效身份证件、同名银行存折（卡）前往银行网点填写《大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务申请表》并签署《中信银行银商通业务客户服务协议书》。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户变更银行结算账号</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户在银行柜面办理托管账号的变更。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">需要按照以下流程办理——个人客户持有效身份证件、新旧银行存折（卡）前往银行网点填写《大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务申请表》。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户撤销签约</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户在银行柜面办理解约交易。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">客户在需要办理银行账户变更及销户时，需先通过银商转账方式将其在市场方的保证金账户余额清零，客户的保证金账户余额清零后直至重新成功指定结算银行之前不能再发生买卖交易，客户在转账成功后第二个工作日，到乙方办理撤销现有结算银行手续，然后再办理新结算银行的指定手续。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">办理流程——个人客户本人持有效身份证件、同名银行存折（卡）、前往银行网点填写《大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务申请表》。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">柜台入金（个人客户）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户在银行柜面向已在市场端开立的本户名交易保证金账户进行入金交易。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——客户可凭本人身份证、同名银行存折（卡）到银行营业网点，申请办理业务。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">柜台出金（个人客户）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户在银行柜面向已在市场端开立的本户名交易保证金账户进行出金交易。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——客户可凭本人身份证、同名银行存折（卡）到银行营业网点，申请办理业务。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">查询保证金账户余额（个人客户）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">银行柜员应客户要求查询客户在交易所保证金账户上的余额。操作流程由银行柜员完成。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">查询转账明细（个人客户）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">由银行柜员应客户要求查询范围，银行柜员根据屏幕提示输入所要查询的银行资金结算账号，选择交易市场，输入需要查询的起始日期和终止日期（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天），柜员提交成功后，按照提示打印通用凭证。</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">■企业客户签约流程</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1.</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户签约</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户在银行柜面办理大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务签约交易。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——企业客户授权代理人本人持有效身份证及复印件、营业执照复印件、法人机构代码证复印件、授权委托书（见附件</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2-3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">）、法定代表人身份证及复印件（以上资料复印件加盖公章）、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">卡及预留印鉴前往银行网点，填写《大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务申请表》并签署《中信银行银商通业务客户服务协议书》。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户变更银行结算账号</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户在银行柜面办理已绑定大宗商品交易资金结算账号的变更。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——企业客户授权代理人本人持有效身份证及复印件（加盖公章）、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">卡前往银行网点，填写《大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务申请表》</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3.&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户撤销签约</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户在银行柜面办理大宗商品交易系统客户解约交易，需先通过银商转账方式将其在市场方的保证金账户余额清零，客户的保证金账户余额清零后直至重新成功指定结算银行之前不能再发生商品买卖交易，客户在转账成功后第二个工作日，到交易所办理撤销现有结算银行手续，然后再办理新结算银行的指定手续。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——企业客户授权代理人本人持有效身份证件、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">卡前往银行网点填写《大宗商品交易资金结算（银商通）业务申请表》。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">柜台入金（企业客户）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户在银行柜面向已在市场端开立的本户名交易保证金账户进行入金交易。</span><u><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></u><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——企业客户授权代理人本人持有效身份证件、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">卡前往银行网点填写“进账单”和“转账支票”并加盖预留印鉴申请办理入金业务。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">5.&nbsp;</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">柜台出金（企业客户）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">企业客户在银行柜面向已在市场端开立的本户名交易保证金账户进行出金交易。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">操作流程——企业客户授权代理人本人持有效身份证件、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">IC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">卡前往银行网点填写“进账单”并加盖预留印鉴申请办理出金业务。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">6.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">查询保证金账户余额</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">银行柜员应客户要求查询客户在交易所保证金账户上的余额。操作流程由银行柜员完成。</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">7.</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">查询转账明细</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">由银行柜员应客户要求查询范围，银行柜员根据屏幕提示输入所要查询的银行资金结算账号，选择交易市场，输入需要查询的起始日期和终止日期（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">90</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天），柜员提交成功后，按照提示打印通用凭证。</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n		</p>\n	</p>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-indent:2em;\">\n	<br />\n</p>','2013-07-05 16:07:07','本站原创',NULL,12,'2013-07-05 16:07:07',1,'','07/05','常见问题'),(349,'交通银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程','<div align=\"center\">\n	<p>\n		<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" height=\"400\" width=\"442\" />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p align=\"left\">\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天津贵金属交易所在交行系统的市场代码为：</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\">100004</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人客户开通银期转帐业务操作代码：</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\">475130</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">交通银行签约业务受理的时间为：</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">09:30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">15:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">注意事项</span><span></span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">投资者在交通银行处理结算银行签约业务时，个人投资者必须先在银行开通“</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">银期转帐</span></b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">”业务，然后才能办理结算银行签约业务。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">如发生银行业务人员完全不了解有关业务，可提示银行方面业务人员：查找与现货市场合作的“交银办函</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">[2008]349 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">号文”了解有关业务情况；也可请银行业务人员从银行内网的“公司业务部</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">-</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">银期业务专栏”中查找上线现货市场进度，其中有交易所的有关业务上线公示。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">如发生银行业务人员不了解有关业务操作，可告知签约业务柜台操作代码为：</span><span></span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">“</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">个人签约</span></b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">”的业务操作代码：</span></span><span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span></b></span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">475130</span></b></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（开通银期转账业务）；</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span></span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">474580</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（结算银行签约业务）；</span><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span></span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">100004</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（期货经纪公司编号）</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人投资者在出现交通银行无法进行签约的情况下，可采用以下任一方案解决：</span></b>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">方案</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：银行柜台人员可输入代码“</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">474580</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">”；</span><span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">方案</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">：银行柜台人员可输入一系列代码：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">→回车键→</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">47</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">→回车键→</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">07</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">→回车键→</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">04</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><br />\n</span></span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">“</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">机构签约</span></b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">”的业务操作代码：</span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">474581</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（银期转账业务签约）；</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">投资者也可直接联系交通银行天津分行友谊支行的了解有关业务人员：魏小姐，电话：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">022</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">28353220</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（首选）、</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">022</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">－</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">28353200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（备用）。</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">交易资金划转操作的有效时间如下：每交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9:00 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">17:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交通银行服务协议-左</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Picture/jtbank/2.jpg\"><img alt=\"交通银行服务协议-左\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Picture/jtbank/2.jpg\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a> <br />\n</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交通银行服务协议-右</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Picture/jtbank/3.jpg\"><img alt=\"交通银行服务协议-右\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Picture/jtbank/3.jpg\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a> <br />\n</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">交通银行业务申请表</span>\n		</p>\n		<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n			<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Picture/jtbank/1.jpg\"><img alt=\"交通银行业务申请表\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Picture/jtbank/1.jpg\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a><br />\n</span>\n		</p>\n	</p>\n</div>','2013-07-05 16:07:28','本站原创',NULL,12,'2013-07-05 16:07:28',1,'','07/05','常见问题'),(350,'农业银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程','<div align=\"center\">\n	<p>\n		<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" height=\"400\" width=\"442\" />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p align=\"left\">\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天津贵金属交易所在农行系统的市场代码为：</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#E53333;\">80370000</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\"></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">农业银行签约业务受理的时间为：</span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">09:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">16:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">注意事项</span><span></span></b>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">一、投资者必须在完成农业银行签约后，通过</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">银商通</span></b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">转账系统进行交易资金划转。通过常规的银行汇款、转帐业务等方式从投资者账户划入交易所保证金专用账户的资金，不能作为投资者的交易资金使用。</span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">二、投资者可以通过交易系统、银行柜台、网银等方式实现交易资金划转。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">三、交易资金划转的注意事项：</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、通过交易系统端办理出入金时须输入银行密码。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、机构投资者开通网银功能的，可通过网银办理出入金及查询业务；个人投资者不支持网银功能。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">投资者在农行临柜办理银商通业务服务相关业务时，可告知银行柜员如下提示：</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、提示银行柜员参照农银发</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">[2009]257</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">号文件处理；</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、天津贵金属交易所在农行系统市场代码为：</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">80370000</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">签约操作的有效时间如下：每交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">16:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">资金划转操作的有效时间如下：每交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">8:30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">至</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">16:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">。</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">如农业银行工作人员不清楚具体转账事宜，可以联系天津农业银行总部：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">022 - 2489 1000</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">农业银行银商通业务申请表</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/nonghang_ystyw.png\"><img alt=\"农业银行银商通业务申请表\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/nonghang_ystyw.png\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a> <br />\n</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">农业银行银商通业务客户服务协议书A</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/nonghang_ysta.png\"><img alt=\"农业银行银商通业务客户服务协议书\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/nonghang_ysta.png\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a> <br />\n</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">农业银行银商通业务客户服务协议书B</span>\n	</p>\n	<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"> <a class=\"group1 cboxElement\" href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/nonghang_ystb.png\"><img alt=\"农业银行银商通业务客户服务协议书\" src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/picture/nonghang_ystb.png\" style=\"border:2px solid #999999;width:175px;height:237px;\" /></a>&nbsp;</span>\n	</p>\n<br />\n</div>','2013-07-05 16:07:22','本站原创',NULL,12,'2013-07-05 16:07:22',1,'','07/05','常见问题'),(351,'建设银行办理开户及三方存管业务流程','<p>\n	<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" height=\"521\" width=\"680\" /> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天津贵金属交易所在建行系统的市场代码为：</span><b><span style=\"color:red;font-size:16px;\">1200000045</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">建设银行签约业务受理的时间为：</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">）柜台签约：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">对公业务：交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9:30-12:00&nbsp;13:30-17:00</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（不同银行网点稍有差别）</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">;</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">个人业务：交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">9:30-17:00</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">）网银签约：交易日的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">8:30-22:00</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://166mintai.com/news/show/352\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">《建行三方托管网银、柜台操作指引》</span></span></a> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"></span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">建设银行网银办理时间：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">8:30</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">—</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">22:00</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">建设银行柜面操作流程：</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">一、</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">建设银行柜台签约业务流程：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、个人、机构客户在银行开立账户或持已有的账户；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、客户到会员单位处开立交易账号，并由会员单位工作人员对交易账号进行预签约操作；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、凭在会员单位处开立的交易账号及三方协议等材料到建设银行柜台办理签约；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、办理高版网银，成为建设银行的个人、企业网上银行高级版用户。</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">特别提示：个人客户可跨网点办理签约业务，机构客户必须在开户网点办理签约业务</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">二、个人客户到柜台签约时需要提供资料：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、提交《中国建设银行企业级电子商务支付服务会员申请表》；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、个人身份证件；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、建设银行结算账户；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、会员单位开立的交易账号；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、已签订的《中国建设银行企业级电子商务支付服务三方服务协议》。</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">特别提示：身份证件均需进行身份核查；</span><u><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">三方协议中“投资者指定交易账号”请填写客户建设银行结算账户</span></u></span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">三、机构客户到柜台签约时需要提供资料：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">加盖单位公章和预留印鉴的《中国建设银行企业级电子商务支付服务会员申请表》</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、企业营业执照；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、组织机构代码证；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、法定代表人身份证件；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、经办人身份证件；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、单位授权委托书；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、会员单位开立的交易账号；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、已签订的《中国建设银行企业级电子商务支付服务三方服务协议》。</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">特别提示：办理时需携带证件原件、公章、财务章、法人章；</span><u><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">三方协议中“投资者指定交易账号”请填写客户建设银行结算账户</span></u></span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">四、建行柜台入金业务：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">客户需持建行银行卡、会员单位开立的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">位交易账号、天津贵金属交易所结算账号到建设银行柜台办理入金业务。</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">天津贵金属交易所结算账号：</span><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">12001626601052504594</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">特别提示：为避免出现通过汇款的方式将资金划转到交易所结算账户从而造成错入资金的情况，因此请客户尽量使用市场端或网银入金。</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span></b> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">五、建行柜台不能办理出金业务，出金业务只可通过市场端和网银实现。</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">六、建行柜台解约业务：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">客户在需要办理解约时，需先将其在市场方的保证金账户余额清零，客户在转账成功后第二个工作日，到银行柜台办理解约手续。</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">七、建行银行卡变更业务：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">客户办理银行卡变更需持以下资料到柜台办理：</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、客户身份证；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、重新提交《中国建设银行企业级电子商务支付服务会员申请表》；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;\">、重新签订《中国建设银行企业级电子商务支付服务三方服务协议》；</span> \n</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4</span><span style=\"font-family: