\"font-size:16px;\">招商银行业务办理时间为9：00-----16：30</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">一、签约</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">1、客户持有效证件申请交易账号。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">2、个人客户到招商银行营业网点申请一卡通，机构客户到招商银行营业网点申请单位银行结算账户。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">个人客户：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">可以通过柜台、网上银行进行签约。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">A、柜台签约：开户行所在地任一网点柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">提交本人一卡通、本人有效居民身份证原件、填写《招商银行银商转账业务申请/维护表》一式两联、确认《招商银行银商转账业务规则》。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">B、网上银行：个人网上银行专业版、大众版。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">填写身份证、交易账号、验证取款密码、交易密码。(</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">以下图片仅为举例说明，仅供参考</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs1.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs2.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" /></a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">机构客户：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">开户行营业网点。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">授权代办人持本人有效身份证件原件及复印件、法人授权委托书、法定代表人有效身份证件复印件、《招商银行银商转账业务申请/维护表》一式两联、确认《招商银行银商转账业务规则》。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">机构客户仅限在开户网点柜台申请银商转账业务功能</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">。</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">二、出入金</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">个人客户</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">：网银、柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">网上银行：个人网上银行专业版、大众版</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">柜台：可在任一网点柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">提交已开通银商转账协议的一卡通、《招商银行银商转账业务资金划转申请表》一式两联。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs3.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">机构客户：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">网上企业银行、柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">网银：网上企业银行。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">柜台：可在开户网点柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">提交加盖预留印鉴的《招商银行银商转账业务资金划转申请表》一式两联，入金还须提交付款凭证（支票、贷记凭证）。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">机构客户经办员登录网上企业银行—投资理财—银商转账，经办银商转账业务。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs4.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">机构客户经办银商转账业务，可在下拉框中选择交易类型。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs5.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs5.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" /></a><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs6.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs6.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">机构客户审批员登录网上企业银行—投资理财—银商转账，审批银商转账业务。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs7.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs7.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">机构客户审批银商转账业务，“活期转保证金”可直接点击“同意”或“否决”</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs8.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs8.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">机构客户审批银商转账业务，保证金转活期若同意须录入交易密码，并点击“同意”，若不同意可直接点击“否决”。</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs9.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs9.jpg\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">注：个人客户可以通过柜台、网银调整银商转账资金划转限额，机构客户需到柜台调整</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs10.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs10.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">三、解约</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">个人客户：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">网银、柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">网银：个人网上银行大众版、专业版。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">柜台：开户网行所在地任意网点。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">提交本人一卡通、本人有效居民身份证原件、填写《招商银行银商转账业务申请/维护表》一式两联，申请关闭银商转账业务功能。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">要点：如果客户账户当天有出入金操作，必须在下一工作日才能进行协议关闭操作。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">目前个人客户仅限在开户行所在地任一网点关闭银商转账业务功能。</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs11.png\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://www.mintai166.com/UpLoads/Article/images/zs11.png\" style=\"border:none;\" width=\"666\" /></a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">机构客户：</span></strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">开户网点柜台。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">授权代办人持本人有效身份证件原件及复印件、法人授权委托书、法定代表人有效身份证件复印件、加盖单位公章及法定代表人或授权代表签章 的《招商银行银商转账业务申请/维护表 》（一式二联）。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">开户网点会计柜面申请关闭银商转账业务功能。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">如果客户账户当天办理过出入金操作，必须在下一工作日才能进行协议关闭操作。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">四、改约</span></strong><br />\n<ul style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;color:#000000;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">\n	<li style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;\">\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">招商银行银行卡消磁</span></strong>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">卡片消磁不影响银商转账功能的使用，仅对刷卡、取款业务有影响。</span><br />\n<ul style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;color:#000000;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">\n	<li style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px;\">\n		<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">招商银行银行卡丢失</span></strong>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">如果客户卡片丢失，客户进行卡片挂失时可以选择：</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">1、冻结账户：冻结期间，银商转账功能不能使用，挂失完成后，客户办理重新开卡（卡片号码不变）则不需要重新开通银商转账功能，银商转账功能直接可以使用；</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">2、不冻结账户：则不影响银商转账功能的正常使用。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">3、卡片丢失后，如果客户直接销卡，并办理新卡（卡片号码变更），则需要关闭原卡的银商转账功能，同时重新开通新卡的银商转账功能。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:宋体;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;line-height:26px;background-color:#FEFCF4;\">挂失可以通过柜面和电话银行办理，补卡只能在柜面办理。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"